********************
***	 To compile  ***
********************

Compile and run just works with Oracle JRE 8 actually !


Compile:

Windows :
javac -sourcepath src -d compiled src\sudoku\*.java src\sudoku\gui\javafx\*.java src\sudoku\values\*.java

Linux :
javac -sourcepath src -d compiled src/sudoku/*.java src/sudoku/gui/javafx/*.java src/sudoku/values/*.java


JavaDoc :

javadoc -private -sourcepath src -subpackages sudoku sudoku.values sudoku.gui.javafx -d doc


Jar :

javapackager -createjar -appclass sudoku.Sudoku -srcdir compiled -outdir dist -outfile Sudoku.jar